string.name: emailConfirm_click
string.comment:
emailConfirm_click
Part of the confirmation email upon registering for a Lichess account.
The unique reset link is presented just after this string.

resources.string: Riix laynkan hoose si aad u furtid akoonkaaga Lichess:
Haddii aanad iska diwaan-gelin Lichess uma baahnid farriintan.
Wuu na soo gaadhay codsigii cusboonaysiinta furaha akoonkaagu.
Haddii uu codsigani adiga kaa yimid, riix laynkan hoose. Haddii kale, iska dhaaf farriintan.
Si aad u caddeysid in aad cinwaankan leedahay, fadlan riix laynkan hoose:

Waxaad si guul leh akoon uga samaysatay https://lichess.org.
Waakan boggaagii gaarka ahaa: %1$s. Halkan ka qurxiso %2$s.
Baashaal, oo boqorka colka baallaha ka yaac!
(Lama riixi karo? Ku day in ad laynka toos ugu qortid interneedka!)
Kani waa cinwaan adeeg oo la xidiidha isticmaalkaaga %s.
Si aad noolasoo xidhiidhid, fadlan isticmaal %s.
